44:24.418 --> 44:25.483
Salute.

44:25.485 --> 44:26.552
[crowd] Salute!

44:26.554 --> 44:27.889
[man] Salute.

44:42.135 --> 44:43.471
[Kruger
speaks foreign language]

44:47.041 --> 44:48.110
Blomfeld!

44:54.514 --> 44:56.150
[Blomfeld]
You like my wall, Kruger?

44:57.318 --> 44:59.418
[Kruger] Yeah, I like it.

44:59.420 --> 45:01.887
The <i>kaffirs</i>
are up to something.

45:01.889 --> 45:05.124
You should take the <i>kaffirs</i>
