45:06.094 --> 45:08.429
You know what
"Paradise Lost" is, Kruger?

45:09.563 --> 45:12.063
A nightclub?

45:12.065 --> 45:15.233
It's a poem,
you clutch plate,

45:15.235 --> 45:16.471
about me.

45:21.175 --> 45:23.108
Fuck you.

45:23.110 --> 45:26.047
[indistinct chatter]

45:42.664 --> 45:45.601
[suspenseful music playing]

46:02.583 --> 46:04.219
Aaah!

46:05.286 --> 46:07.954
[siren blaring]

46:07.956 --> 46:10.325
[all shouting]

46:19.967 --> 46:21.300
- [Schmidt] Down!
- [man] Get down.

46:21.302 --> 46:23.605
[Schmidt] Get the fuck down,
you fuckers!

46:26.974 --> 46:28.043
[Schmidt] Down!

46:30.077 --> 46:31.246
[Schmidt] Down!

46:32.746 --> 46:35.149
- Down. Now.
- [dog barks]

46:38.418 --> 46:40.151
Do you want a fucking lockdown,

46:40.153 --> 46:42.420
- you animals?
- [prisoners] No, sir!

46:42.422 --> 46:44.322
[Schmidt] Are there rules here,
you bastards?

46:44.324 --> 46:46.258
[prisoners] Yes, sir!

46:46.260 --> 46:48.126
Whose fucking rules are they?

46:48.128 --> 46:49.195
[prisoners] Yours, sir!

46:49.197 --> 46:50.463
Whose fucking rules are they?

46:50.465 --> 46:51.530
[prisoners] Yours, sir!

46:51.532 --> 46:52.630
Don't you forget it.

46:52.632 --> 46:54.166
