to know

01:54:13.503 --> 01:54:15.202
I never took you
for granted.

01:54:15.204 --> 01:54:16.470
Never.

01:54:16.472 --> 01:54:19.074
[Leah] Why, you old goat,

01:54:19.076 --> 01:54:21.543
