for forgiveness?

01:54:21.545 --> 01:54:22.643
[Tutu]
I suppose I am.

01:54:22.645 --> 01:54:23.812
[Leah laughs]

01:54:23.814 --> 01:54:25.379
[Tutu] Look at it.

01:54:25.381 --> 01:54:27.281
